  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_llm-raw-the-eye-o.O-Something%27s%20Cooking.pdf_4_2",
    "text": "Possessions: Masterwork steak knife, potion of cure moderate wounds, potion of endurance, ring of protection +1, masterwork cookware (+2 circumstance bonus on Profession [cook] checks).",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
