    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_llm-raw-the-eye-o.O-Something%27s%20Cooking.pdf_4_28",
    "text": "Spurt (Ex): If the calzone golem is struck for damage by a slashing or piercing weapon, it spurts out a small splash of extremely hot juices from the wound. This spurt inflicts 1 point of fire damage to all individuals within 5 feet of the golem.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
